# CSS Selector Types

    h1            Select all <h1> elements
    .class        Select all elements with class
    #id           Select all elements with #id
    *             Select all elements
    div, p        Select all <div> and <p> elements
    div > p       Select all <p> elements, that are a direct descendant of a <div>
    div + p       Select all <p> elements, that are next sibling (placed directly after) a <div> element
    